            <div class="faq_divider"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq_block">
            <div class="faq_top">
              <h3 class="h4">What will you Social Connect do with my data after I connect my Instagram account?</h3><img src="https://ybhltd.com/fanse/images/down.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Chevron" class="faq_arrow">
            </div>
            <div class="faq_bottom">
              <div class="faq_text">We will only share your post and audience insights to brands that you have given permission to. <br></div>
