          </div>
          <div class="faq_block">
            <div class="faq_top">
              <h3 class="h4">Why should I use Social Connect and not just send a screenshot?</h3><img src="https://ybhltd.com/fanse/images/down.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Chevron" class="faq_arrow">
            </div>
